## Weekly File Column Layout Structure

**CRITICAL**: All weekly files MUST use the multi-column layout structure. This makes content significantly easier to read by organizing information horizontally.

### Structure for Each Day

Each day section MUST be formatted with columns using this structure:

```markdown
## [Day] YYYY-MM-DD

<div class="columns">

<div class="column">

### Daily Habits
- [ ] LinkedIn post
- [ ] 2 LinkedIn comments  
- [ ] Workout

</div>

